metadata.name: Loosing Touch With Reality
metadata.description:
One of one NFT by Jesse Travis, gives you full ownership of this physical canvas. You can choose to have the canvas shipped to you, donated or destroyed. This original painting will live forever on the blockchain but you decide its physical fate. 

Acrylics, spray paint and oil on 24" by 36" canvas. Coated in crystal clear epoxy resin.

Original one of one painting, comes with certificate of authenticity. This painting's life is in your hands, choose wisely.
